headline: Electronic Arts to Report Q2 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: EA anticipates Q2 fiscal 2026 net bookings of $1.8B-$1.9 billion, facing an 8-point American football headwind, offset by Madden NFL 26 launch and Apex Legends momentum.
